Sounds like your diagnosis is correct.  Buy a new cooler (get the right
kind for the engine and shroud) and seals.  Remove engine, remove tin,
replace cooler, replace tin, replace engine.

It _might_ be the seals only, but if you don't buy the cooler you won't
have one on the weekend!

